  speakers:
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 0b3e78cb05549499aad3a84345f2f016, type: 2}
  - {fileID: 11400000, guid: c4de1d89e1c984af5892c57c606847c0, type: 2}
  entries:
  - speakerIndex: 0
    text: Hello there! Check this, to interact I have to press [interact]! That is
      crazy, isn't it?
  - speakerIndex: 1
    text: Well I do not have to press [interact] to do something! That is your problem
      since you are a non NPC. I do whatever...
  - speakerIndex: 0
    text: So am I a puppet?
  - speakerIndex: 1
    text: Yes. And a bad one, since I am going to destroy you and your puppet master
      without the need of pressing [interact] to do anything.
  - speakerIndex: 0
    text: Oh damn...
